original_title: England's Six of the Best - The Nineties
overview: Six key matches for the England Rugby squad are collected here, from various points in the 1990s. The games included are: England's win over South Africa in 1998; England's draw with New Zealand in 1997; England's win over Australia in 1995; England's win over South Africa in 1994; England's 24 - 0 win over Wales in 1992; and England's win over France in 1991. Includes classic footage of Rob Andrew, Clive Woodward, Matt Dawson, Rory Underwood, and many others, in action upon the pitch.
title: England's Six of the Best - The Nineties
